cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and image processing, specifically on removing moire patterns from digital images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves some graphics-related concepts, such as pixel grids and interference, which could place it under cs.GR (Graphics).
